Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures

Class AbstractTree

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.AbstractTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseOpsInt, TreeOpsInt, TreeSearchOps, TreeTraversalOps
public abstract class AbstractTree extends Object implements TreeOpsInt, TreeTraversalOps, TreeSearchOps

Title: AbstractTree

Description:

Abstract template for any general tree structure. TreeOpsInt, TreeTraversalOps and TreeSearchOps are inherited to layout the framework for the abstract class. This class can be inherited to allow for easy and standardized implementation of a tree
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
